   <text>
      <body>
         <div>
            <head>4.11.1880 Donnerstag</head>
            <p>
               <placeName type="write" key="49097">Ascot</placeName> 4<hi rend="ul.2">
                  <hi rend="sup">th</hi>
               </hi> November 1880 Thursday.</p>
            <p>Today Bonnemaman<note type="reg">
                  <persName key="362">Lynch, Caroline</persName>
               </note> came to see me and brought me a dreadful shock. Poor dear Grandmama<note type="reg">
                  <persName key="744">Kessler, Henriette</persName>
               </note> in <placeName key="49069">Hamburg</placeName> is dead from a fall which she
               had on Monday and which proved fatal. To think that an unfortunate step can bring
               death! <persName key="176">Papa</persName> is in <placeName key="49069">Hamburg</placeName> because as soon as he heard of the accident he went there. I
               hope it will not shake him too greatly for he loved her so dearly! and she was so
               good. She died on the 2<hi rend="ul.2">
                  <hi rend="sup">d</hi>
               </hi> of November</p>
         </div>
